Thank you Chow for always pushing the students to pursue their talents and their dreams.

Still buzzing from all the incredible energy at Spectra 2025!💥
 
Shoutout to our community of students, instructors and our team at ARDS for making this event a huge success!💫

Here's to many more Spectra🏆

Thrilled to announce the runner-up at Spectra2025! 🥈

Hats off to the hard work, dedication, and passion, of this batch. 

-Choreography by @divya_easwaran

-Assistant choreographer @_dipss09

A massive shoutout to all the participants that made this magic show "magic" indeed💫

A stunning blend of choreography and creativity, with a touch of illusion — this performance truly danced on another level. 🔥✨

From sharp moves to smooth transitions, every beat was hit with precision. The grind, the passion, the rhythm — this batch brought it all and then some.

Proud to announce the Runner-Up of Spectra 2025 — Open Style Batch!
@divya_easwaran
Assistant Choreographer @_dipss09

You didn’t just perform — you owned the stage.
